# StartBusiness Demo Website - Tech Stack

## Frontend Framework
- Next.js 14 (App Router)
- React 18
- TypeScript

## UI and Styling
- Tailwind CSS for styling
- shadcn/ui component library
- Lucide React for icons
- Framer Motion for animations
- Mobile-first, responsive design

## State Management
- React useState/useReducer for local state
- Zustand for global client state (when needed)

## Authentication
- Custom OTP-based authentication system
- Email/SMS login without passwords

## Database
- PostgreSQL
- Prisma ORM for database access

## Key Features
- Business Registration Services
- Company Incorporation
- Trademark & Copyright Services
- Compliance Management
- Blog with Featured Posts
- WhatsApp Integration
- Contact Form

## Key Libraries
- next/image for optimized images
- next/link for client-side navigation
- framer-motion for animations
- lucide-react for icons
- @vercel/blob for image storage

## Deployment
- Vercel for hosting
- Automatic deployments from v0.dev
- GitHub integration for version control